arcade.agent.helper

Class MakeCARTHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.agent.helper.CARTHelper
      • arcade.agent.helper.MakeCARTHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Helper, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable

    public class MakeCARTHelper
extends CARTHelper
    Extension of CARTHelper for cell division. Adapted from MakeTissueHelper.

    MakeCARTHelper is repeatedly stepped from its creation until either the cell is no longer able to proliferate or it has successfully doubled in size and is able to create a new cell object.
